    <note>Missing required fields; violates schema constraints for `llm-hallucination-test-patterns` (e.g. empty / placeholder owner, fewer items than minItems, missing evidence_quote / anti_output / exit_criterion as applicable). Validator rejects with explicit violation list.</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <pattern>any field with value 'TBD' / 'TODO' / 'FIXME'</pattern>
    <pattern>'team' / 'we' as owner</pattern>
    <pattern>free-form prose where a structured field is required</pattern>
    <pattern>LLM-judge-only labels</pattern>
    <pattern>per-pattern n&lt;10</pattern>
  </section>

